{
  "number": 874,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/874",
  "title": "add a debounce option to the searchBox",
  "body": "After much thinking, even the searchHook will not be the right solution to implement debounce ONLY at the searchbox level.\n\nThe search hook will only be able to debounce globally, which is not what we are looking for.\n\nSo we should provide an option to debounce the searchBox, mostly for those reasons:\n- very heavy interfaces (lot of facets, lot of images, ..)\n- mobile experiences\n\nWe could implement a searchBox hook but I feel like everyone will then have to reimplement his own debounce, and users might not even know what is a debounce, or how to implement one or use one correctly.\n\nJust import {debounce} from lodash should be sufficient.\n",
